Class AbstractBooleanBigList

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BigList<java.lang.Boolean>, BooleanBigList, BooleanCollection, BooleanIterable, BooleanStack, Size64, Stack<java.lang.Boolean>, java.lang.Comparable<BigList<? extends java.lang.Boolean>>, java.lang.Iterable<java.lang.Boolean>, java.util.Collection<java.lang.Boolean>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractBooleanBigList.BooleanSubList, BooleanBigArrayBigList, BooleanBigLists.ListBigList, BooleanBigLists.Singleton

    public abstract class AbstractBooleanBigList
extends AbstractBooleanCollection
implements BooleanBigList, BooleanStack
    An abstract class providing basic methods for big lists implementing a type-specific big list interface.
